Graphics
- [] Texture mapping
- [] Anti-aliasing
- [] Animations

Gameplay
- [] Networking (multiplayer)
- [] Procedural generation
- [] Raycasting (getting entity/object in crosshair or projectiles)
- [] Physics engine (collisions, gravity, etc)

Performance
- [] GPU rendering using OpenGL/DirectX/Vulkan
- [] Compiled models (not having to process models on every game launch)

Misc
- [] Fully custom 2D UI system (not piggybacking off AWT's 2D drawing tools)
- [] Sound engine
